            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve the<strong> beef stock mix</strong> in 275ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the onions have caramelised, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>plain flour </strong>and cook for 30 sec or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, transfer to a small bowl and set aside for later</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1646999777633-x200.jpg",
