            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken breast portions</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Once golden, reduce the heat to medium and add the <strong>beef stock</strong>, <strong>caramelised onion </strong>and <strong>dried basil</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook, covered, for 12-15 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1646999781566-x200.jpg",
